喜怒无常的布鲁斯与翅膀乐团的丹尼·莱恩去世，享年 79 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/denny-laine-of-the-moody-blues-and-wings-has-died-ged-79-3553917?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=denny-laine-喜怒无常的蓝调与翅膀之人已于 79 岁去世Alex RigottiTue, 05 Dec 2023 20:16:06 +0000 Music NewsNews..Rock https://www.nme.com/?p=3553917 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="丹尼·莱恩（Al Pereira/Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位音乐家在与间质性肺病（ILD）长期斗争后去世</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/denny-laine-of-the-moody-blues-and-wings-has-died-aged-79-3553917">The Moody Blues and Wings 乐队主唱 Denny Laine 去世，享年 79 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="丹尼·莱恩（Al Pereira/Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Denny-Laine-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-moody-blues">穆迪布鲁斯</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wings">​​翅膀乐队</a>成员丹尼·莱恩去世，享年 79 岁。</p><p>他的妻子伊丽莎白·海因斯在社交媒体上发布了这一消息，称莱恩因间质性肺病（ILD）去世。 “我亲爱的丈夫今天清晨平静地去世了，”她开始说道。</p><p> “他和我都相信他会克服健康障碍，回到康复中心并最终回家，”她继续说道。 “不幸的是，他的肺病——间质性肺病（ILD）是不可预测的、具有侵袭性的；每次感染都会削弱并损害他的肺部。他每天都在战斗。他是如此坚强和勇敢，从不抱怨。他只想回家和我在一起，还有他的宠物小猫查理，弹着吉普赛吉他。”</p><p>海因斯表示，莱恩“非常感谢”他在“健康危机”期间得到的爱和支持。她写道：“我绝对荣幸和荣幸，不仅能成为他的妻子，还能在他生病和脆弱时照顾他。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0endijr_aN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C56