1427" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3451427" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3451427" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wide-awake-festival-4.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wide-awake-festival-4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wide-awake-festival-4-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wide-awake-festival-4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wide-awake-festival-4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wide-awake-festival-4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wide-awake-festival-4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3451427" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：加里·琼斯</figcaption></figure><p>去年的演出中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caroline-polachek">卡罗琳·波拉切克（Caroline Polachek）</a>登上舞台，成为头条新闻， <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/festivals-blog/wide-awake-festival-south-london-caroline-polachek-3450008"><em>《NME》</em>将这场表演称为</a>“大胆的预订决定”，但“值得称赞的表演，带来了丰厚的回报；”她完成了这个重要的里程碑时刻。”</p><p>她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-segall">泰·西格尔 (Ty Segall)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thee-oh-sees">奥西斯 (Osees</a> )、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/a-place-to-bury-strangers">埋葬陌生人的地方 (A Place To Bury Strangers)</a>和埃罗尔·阿尔坎<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/erol-alkan">(Erol Alkan)</a>一起参加了一场<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/festivals-blog/wide-awake-festival-south-london-caroline-polachek-3450008">四星级的音乐节表演</a>：“尽管音乐节的‘反文化’资格让人感觉有点可疑（昂贵的 Brewdog 酒吧和其他各种音乐节）网站周围的大品牌存在很难引起反叛），Wide Awake 确实成功地整合了一个完全独特的法案，在一个非常拥挤的领域中脱颖而出。”</p><p>在 Slowdive 的其他新闻中，乐队宣布了 2024 年英国/欧洲的一系列演出日期。他们将于 1 月在阿姆斯特丹出发，于 2 月 17 日访问伦敦的 Eventim Apollo，并于 2 月 27 日在曼彻斯特学院结束。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/slowdive-tickets/artist/2015858?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=zdmQRZTfwxyNUAZWPp1MB0h4UkFyBHTlnTmkXI0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找所有门票。</p><p>乐队还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slowdive-new-single-alife-announce-2024-uk-european-tour-buy-tickets-3491462">发行了他们的新单曲《alife》</a> ，其中歌手、作词家和吉他手尼尔·霍尔斯特德 (Neil Halstead) 表示：“《alife》是我们为唱片完成的首批歌曲之一。肖恩·埃弗雷特 (Shawn Everett) 的混音工作非常出色。我们尝试了很多次，想要自己找出一个好的组合，但是却做不到。 。 。直到肖恩介入之前，我们都被打败了。</p><p> “我们决定如果他能处理好这个问题，他可能就能完成整张唱片。我们的朋友 Jake Nelson 为这首歌制作了非常漂亮的动画；它从艺术品中提取了一些图像，并对其进行了更深入的挖掘。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slowdive-modeselektor-and-more-join-wide-awake-2024-line-up-3553893">Slowdive、Modeselektor 等加入 Wide Awake 2024 的阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Bolis Pupul 分享新单曲《Completely Half》并宣布与 Soulwax 联合制作的首张专辑《Letter To Yu》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/bolis-pupul-shares-new-single-completely-half-and-announces-soulwax-productd-debut-album-letter-to-yu-35538​​85?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bolis-pupul-shares-new-single-completely-half-and-announces-soulwax-producted-debut-album-letter-to-yuAnagricel Duran Tue, 05 Dec 2023 18:20:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=35538​​85 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Bolis Pupul 于 2022 年 7 月 10 日在英国伦敦海德公园举行的美国运通 BST 海德公园演出。 （摄影：Burak Cingi/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张唱片被描述为一封写给他母亲的情书，他的母亲于 2008 年因交通事故去世</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bolis-pupul-shares-new-single-completely-half-and-announces-soulwax-produced-debut-album-letter-to-yu-3553885">Bolis Pupul 分享了新单曲“Completely Half”，并宣布 Soulwax 联合制作的首张专辑“Letter To Yu”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Bolis Pupul 于 2022 年 7 月 10 日在英国伦敦海德公园举行的美国运通 BST 海德公园演出。 （摄影：Burak Cingi/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/bolis-pupul">Bolis Pupul</a>宣布了他的首张唱片“Letter To Yu”，并分享了其主打单曲“Completely Half”。看看下面的视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlotte-adigery-and-bolis-pupul-share-ceci-nest-pas-un-cliche-detail-us-tour-3150524">夏洛特·阿迪格里 (Charlotte Adigéry) 和波利斯·普普尔 (Bolis Pupul) – 《主题舞者》评论：欢乐、幽默的热潮</a></strong></li></ul><p>《给于的信》被描述为一封写给他2008年因交通事故去世的母亲的情书。普普尔的父亲是比利时人，母亲是中国人。母亲去世后，普普尔开始拥抱并接受他的传统。</p><p> “当我开始思考我的根源时，我不再为它们感到羞耻，而是开始拥抱它们，”他说（根据<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/bolis-pupul-announces-his-soulwax-produced-debut-album-letter-to-yu" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>“最适合的线</em></a>”）。 “因此，与他们取得联系对我来说变得越来越重要。我在比利时上夜校并开始学习中文。我这样做了四年。这是第一步。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bolis Pupul - Completely Half（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YQfCWB-TOrg?start=3&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Completley Half》的视频由 Magnum 摄影师 Bieke Depoorter 在香港市中心拍摄，视频中 Pupul 探索这座中国城市的街道和建筑物，寻找他已故的母亲。</p><p>谈到创作首张唱片的经历，Pupul 表示（根据<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/bolis-pupul-announces-his-soulwax-produced-debut-album-letter-to-yu" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Line of Best Fit</em></a> ）“尽管这次旅行非常激动，有时也很悲伤，但我也度过了一些让我非常开心的美好时光。这产生了非常令人振奋的旋律，让我觉得我可以掌控自己的生活。”</p><p> 《Letter To Yu》将于 3 月 8 日通过<a href="/artists/soulwax">Soulwax</a>的唱片公司 Deewee 发行。这对比利时电子摇滚二人组与 Pupul 共同制作了这张唱片。<a href="https://bolispupul.lnk.to/letter-to-yu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订专辑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0Oqqnutji0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41